trans-unit.source: Provides the basic interface between a tracking service and the run-time tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Gir grunnleggende grensesnittet mellom en Sporingstjenesten og infrastruktur for kjøring sporing.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A tracking service is responsible for supplying tracking channels and tracking profiles to the workflow run-time engine.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]En Sporingstjenesten er ansvarlig for oppgir sporing kanaler og sporing profiler til arbeidsflyten kjøretid-motoren.

trans-unit.source: The workflow run-time engine requests one <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> from a tracking service for each workflow instance for which it has a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.
trans-unit.target: Arbeidsflyten kjøretid motoren ber om en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>fra en Sporingstjenesten for hver arbeidsflytforekomsten som den har en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>

trans-unit.source: The workflow run-time engine uses this <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> to send tracking records associated with that workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Motoren for arbeidsflyten kjøretid bruker denne <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>sende sporing poster som er knyttet til denne arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> contains track points that specify a set of tracking events for which the run-time tracking infrastructure should send tracking records.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>inneholder spor punkt som angir et sett med hendelser som kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur skal sende sporing oppføringer for sporing.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> may also specify data to be extracted from the workflow instance when one of these tracking events occurs.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>kan også angi dataene som skal trekkes ut arbeidsflytforekomsten når en av disse sporing hendelser inntreffer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: The run-time tracking infrastructure uses a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> to filter tracking events emitted by a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur bruker en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>Filter sporing hendelser slippes ut av en arbeidsflytforekomst.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: When a tracking event is emitted that matches a track point in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, the run-time tracking infrastructure extracts any data specified in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> from the workflow instance and encapsulates this data and information about the tracking event in a tracking record.
trans-unit.target: Når en hendelse for sporing er slippes ut som samsvarer med et Sporingspunkt i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur trekker ut alle data som er angitt i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>fra arbeidsflytforekomsten og innkapsler denne data og informasjon om hendelsen sporing i en oppføring for sporing.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: This tracking record is then sent over the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> associated with the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Denne oppføring sporing deretter sendes via den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>knyttet til arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>

trans-unit.source: A tracking record may be one of the following kinds: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> The host application can use the tracking record in any way that it chooses.
trans-unit.target: Sporing kan være én av følgende: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>vertsprogrammet kan bruke sporing oppføringen i en slik måte at den velger.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: For example, the host application may store the tracking information in a database and use it to implement a sophisticated user interface, or it may use the information to inform an administrator of a condition that requires some action.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel vertsprogrammet kan lagre sporingsinformasjonen i en database og bruke den til å implementere et avansert brukergrensesnitt, eller den kan bruke informasjonen til å informere administrator i en tilstand som krever en handling.

trans-unit.source: You can register a tracking service with the workflow run-time engine by calling <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.AddService%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or by including the appropriate entry in the application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Du kan registrere en Sporingstjenesten med arbeidsflyten kjøretid motoren ved å kalle <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.AddService%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller ved å inkludere riktig oppføring i programmets konfigurasjonsfil.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.AddService%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: All tracking services must inherit from the TrackingService abstract class.
trans-unit.target: Sporing tjenestene må arve fra den TrackingService abstrakt klassen.

trans-unit.source: This class defines the basic interface between a tracking service and the run-time tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen definerer grunnleggende grensesnittet mellom en Sporingstjenesten og infrastruktur for kjøring sporing.

trans-unit.source: The workflow run-time engine requests a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> for a specific workflow instance or workflow <xref:System.Type> by calling one of the overloaded <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetProfile%2A> methods or the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryGetProfile%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Arbeidsflyten kjøretid motoren forespørsler en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>for en bestemt arbeidsflytforekomst eller arbeidsflyt <xref:System.Type>ved å kalle en av de overbelastet <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetProfile%2A>metoder eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryGetProfile%2A>metode.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryGetProfile%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetProfile%2A> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: The workflow run-time engine calls <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetTrackingChannel%2A> to request a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>.
trans-unit.target: Arbeidsflyten kjøretid motoren kall <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetTrackingChannel%2A>å be om en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetTrackingChannel%2A>

trans-unit.source: The workflow tracking runtime calls the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetProfile%2A> and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryGetProfile%2A> methods whenever a workflow instance is created or loaded from the persistence store.
trans-unit.target: Arbeidsflyten sporing runtime kall av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetProfile%2A>og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryGetProfile%2A>metoder når en arbeidsflytforekomst som er opprettet eller lastet inn fra vedvarende lager.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryGetProfile%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.GetProfile%2A>

trans-unit.source: The overhead associated with these calls can be costly to the tracking service (many database calls, for example).
trans-unit.target: Overhead tilknyttet kallene kan være vanskelig å Sporingstjenesten (mange databasen kall, for eksempel).

trans-unit.source: You can implement the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification> interface in your tracking service to circumvent this call-based mechanism and use events to notify the workflow runtime engine of changes to a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan implementere <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>grensesnittet i din Sporingstjenesten å omgå dette kallet kodebasert mekanisme og bruke hendelser for å varsle arbeidsflyten runtime motoren om endringer i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>

trans-unit.source: For tracking services that implement the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification> interface, the workflow run-time engine subscribes to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated> and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> events.
trans-unit.target: For å spore tjenester som implementerer den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>grensesnittet arbeidsflyten kjøretid motoren abonnerer på den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated>og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>hendelser.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>

trans-unit.source: Your tracking service can raise the appropriate event when a change to one of its tracking profiles occurs.
trans-unit.target: Din Sporingstjenesten kan øke riktig hendelse når en endring i ett av sporing profilene oppstår.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> class implements this interface.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>klassen implementerer dette grensesnittet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: The workflow run-time engine calls the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryReloadProfile%2A> method to test whether a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> has been updated or removed as a result of an explicit call by a host or a service to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.ReloadTrackingProfiles%2A> on a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Arbeidsflyten kjøretid motoren kall av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryReloadProfile%2A>metode for å teste om en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>er oppdatert eller fjernet som følge av et eksplisitt kall av vert eller en tjeneste som <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.ReloadTrackingProfiles%2A>på en arbeidsflytforekomst.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.ReloadTrackingProfiles%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService.TryReloadProfile%2A>

trans-unit.source: This process enables a host or service to dynamically change the tracking profile that is being used for a specific workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør det mulig et vertsnavn eller en tjeneste endre dynamisk sporing-profil som brukes for en bestemt arbeidsflytforekomst.

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Når implementert i en avledet klasse, initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingService"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Must be overridden in the derived class, and when implemented, returns the tracking profile for the specified workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Må overstyres i den utledede klassen, og når implementert, returnerer sporing profilen for den angitte arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: A tracking service is responsible for managing the tracking profiles available for specific workflow types and specific workflow instances.
trans-unit.target: En Sporingstjenesten er ansvarlig for behandling av sporing-profiler som er tilgjengelige for spesifikk arbeidsflyttyper og bestemte arbeidsflytforekomster.

trans-unit.source: You can implement this management in whatever manner you choose.
trans-unit.target: Du kan implementere denne administrasjonspakken på måten du velger.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can return the same <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> for every workflow <xref:System.Type> and workflow instance; or you can manage a sophisticated store of tracking profiles referenced by workflow instance, workflow <xref:System.Type>, and <xref:System.Version>.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel kan du gå tilbake samme <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>for hver arbeidsflyt <xref:System.Type>og arbeidsflytforekomsten; eller du kan administrere en avansert butikk for å spore profiler refererer til arbeidsflytforekomsten, arbeidsflyt <xref:System.Type>, og <xref:System.Version>.</xref:System.Version> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Guid> of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Guid>til arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Guid>

trans-unit.source: The tracking profile for the specified workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Profilen sporing for den angitte arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Must be overridden in the derived class, and when implemented, returns the tracking profile, qualified by version, for the specified workflow <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: Må overstyres i den utledede klassen, og når implementert, returnerer sporing-profil kvalifisert av versjon for den angitte arbeidsflyten <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A tracking service is responsible for managing the tracking profiles available for specific workflow types and specific workflow instances.
trans-unit.target: En Sporingstjenesten er ansvarlig for behandling av sporing-profiler som er tilgjengelige for spesifikk arbeidsflyttyper og bestemte arbeidsflytforekomster.

trans-unit.source: You can implement this management in whatever manner you choose.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can return the same <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> for every workflow <xref:System.Type> and workflow instance; or you can manage a sophisticated store of tracking profiles referenced by workflow instance, workflow <xref:System.Type>, and <xref:System.Version>.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel kan du gå tilbake samme <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>for hver arbeidsflyt <xref:System.Type>og arbeidsflytforekomsten; eller du kan administrere en avansert butikk for å spore profiler refererer til arbeidsflytforekomsten, arbeidsflyt <xref:System.Type>, og <xref:System.Version>.</xref:System.Version> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>av arbeidsflyten.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Version> of the tracking profile.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Version>av sporing profilen.</xref:System.Version>

trans-unit.source: The tracking profile for the specified workflow type.
trans-unit.target: Profilen sporing for den angitte arbeidsflyttypen.

trans-unit.source: Must be overridden in the derived class, and when implemented, returns the channel that the run-time tracking infrastructure uses to send tracking records to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Må overstyres i den utledede klassen, og når implementert, returnerer kanalen som kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur bruker til å sende sporing poster til Sporingstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The run-time tracking infrastructure uses one <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> for each tracking service for each workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur bruker en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>for hver Sporingstjenesten for hver arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>

trans-unit.source: The workflow run-time engine calls GetTrackingChannel on each tracking service to get the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> for that service.
trans-unit.target: Motoren for arbeidsflyten kjøretid kaller GetTrackingChannel på hver Sporingstjenesten å hente den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>for tjenesten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>

trans-unit.source: You can use the information passed in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingParameters> to associate tracking data sent on the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> for your tracking service with a particular root workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke informasjonen innsendte <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingParameters>å knytte sporing data sendes på den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>for av Sporingstjenesten med en bestemt roten arbeidsflytforekomst.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingParameters>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingParameters"></xref> associated with the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingParameters"> </xref> knyttet til arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel"></xref> that is used to send tracking records to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel"> </xref> som brukes til å sende sporing poster til Sporingstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Must be overridden in the derived class, and when implemented, retrieves the tracking profile for the specified workflow type if one is available.
trans-unit.target: Må overstyres i den utledede klassen, og når implementert, henter sporing profilen for den angitte arbeidsflyttypen Hvis det er tilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: You can implement this management in whatever manner you choose.

trans-unit.target: For eksempel kan du gå tilbake samme <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>for hver arbeidsflyt <xref:System.Type>og arbeidsflytforekomsten; eller du kan administrere en avansert butikk for å spore profiler refererer til arbeidsflytforekomsten, arbeidsflyt <xref:System.Type>, og <xref:System.Version>.</xref:System.Version> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: Must be overridden in the derived class, and when implemented, retrieves a new tracking profile for the specified workflow instance if the tracking profile has changed since it was last loaded.
trans-unit.target: Må overstyres i den utledede klassen, og når implementert, henter en ny sporing-profil for den angitte arbeidsflytforekomsten Hvis sporing profilen er endret siden den sist ble lastet inn.

trans-unit.source: TryReloadProfile is called by the run-time tracking infrastructure to determine whether a new <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> should be loaded for the specified workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: TryReloadProfile kalles ved kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur for å fastslå om en ny <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>må være lastet inn for den angitte arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: If a new <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> is required, it is returned in `profile`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en ny <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>er nødvendig, returneres i `profile`.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: If you want the run-time tracking infrastructure to stop tracking a workflow instance, your tracking service should return `true` and set `profile` equal to a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur for å stoppe sporing av en arbeidsflytforekomst, din sporingstjenesten skal returnere `true` og `profile` lik en nullreferanse (`Nothing` i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Your tracking service can use `workflowType` or `workflowInstanceId` in whatever manner you choose to determine whether a tracking profile should be reloaded.
trans-unit.target: Din Sporingstjenesten kan bruke `workflowType` eller `workflowInstanceId` på måten du vil finne ut om en sporing profil skal lastes inn på nytt.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> only uses `workflowInstanceId` to decide whether the tracking profile should be reloaded.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>bare bruker `workflowInstanceId` til å avgjøre om sporing profilen skal lastes inn på nytt.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: TryReloadProfile is called by the run-time tracking infrastructure according to its own tracking semantics, or in response to the host or a service calling <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.ReloadTrackingProfiles%2A?displayProperty=fullName> on a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: TryReloadProfile kalles ved kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur i henhold til sin egen sporing semantikk eller som svar på verten eller en tjeneste-kaller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.ReloadTrackingProfiles%2A?displayProperty=fullName>på en arbeidsflytforekomst.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.ReloadTrackingProfiles%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
